        "id": 5649
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-10T17:24:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Ah. \"apply the update\" -- I guess B is some delta applied to A? Can the delta be rotated? (I hadn\u0027t thought about this aspect).",
      "parentUuid": "5acbeffa_66d9321e",
      "revId": "f369f74111f0522df8f06d4b1d86b87f5dfc1167",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "7f9b8517_843bf0c3",
        "filename": "/PATCHSET_LEVEL",
        "patchSetId": 2
      },
      "lineNbr": 0,
      "author": {
